Enum Class CommProtocol

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CommProtocol>
us.mn.state.dot.tms.CommProtocol
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CommProtocol>, Constable
public enum CommProtocol extends Enum<CommProtocol>
Communication protocol enumeration. The ordinal values correspond to the records in the iris.comm_protocol look-up table.
Author:
Douglas Lau, Michael Darter, John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting
